To compile wspr you will need:
* libfftw
* portaudio
* gfortran or g95
* matplotlib
* scipy
* pymc ??
* readline
* ipython ??
* nose (numpy)
* DateUtils
* numpy (f2py)
* python imaging
* libsamplerate
* hamlib


MAC OSX
=======
* Install xcode (1)
* Install portaudio (2)
* Install gfortran (or g95)
* Install Fortran2Python
 sudo port install py-numpy

(1) http://developer.apple.com/support/mac/tools
(2) http://www.portaudio.com/download.html
